ttp_template:
<group name="address_domain_name_mail_server_priority">
Domain Name: {{DOMAIN_NAME | ORPHRASE}}
Address:  {{ADDRESS | ORPHRASE}}
Query Type:  {{QUERY_TYPE | ORPHRASE}}
Mail Server: {{MAIL_SERVER | ORPHRASE}}
Priority:  {{PRIORITY | ORPHRASE}}
TTL:  {{TTL | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value QUERY_TYPE (\S+)
Value DOMAIN_NAME (\S+)
Value ADDRESS (\S+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value MAIL_SERVER (\S+)
Value PRIORITY (\d+)

Start
  ^Query\s+Type:\s+${QUERY_TYPE}\s*$$
  ^Domain\s+Name:\s+${DOMAIN_NAME}\s*$$
  ^Address:\s+${ADDRESS}\s*$$
  ^TTL:\s+${TTL}\s*$$
  ^Mail\s+Server:\s+${MAIL_SERVER}\s*$$
  ^Priority:\s+${PRIORITY}\s*$$ -> Record
